Package com.sicomsa.dmt.solicitude.batch

Class Batch.DownloadHandler

java.lang.Object
com.sicomsa.dmt.solicitude.batch.Batch.DownloadHandler
All Implemented Interfaces:
DownloadListener, EventListener
Enclosing class:
Batch
protected static class Batch.DownloadHandler extends Object implements DownloadListener
Implementation of DownloadListener that uses a specified BatchWriter to write all download events that are notified to it.

If there is any SOAPException or IOException throw while writing to the batch file, a DownloadEventException will be re-thrown wrapping the original cause of the exception.
